HEADWORD: Exserted
<hw>Ex*sert"ed</hw>, }</mhw>
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>exsertus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>exserere</ets>
to stretch out or forth. See <er>Exert</er>.]</ety> <def>Standing out;
projecting beyond some other part; <as>as, <ex>exsert</ex>
